## Polyglot Persistence Rules
- **MongoDB**: lưu `POSTS`, `COMMENTS` (content-heavy, read-many).
- **PostgreSQL**: lưu `FOLLOWS`, `POST_LIKES`, `POST_SAVES`, `COMMENT_REACTION`, `OUTBOX_EVENTS`, `SEARCH_HISTORY`, user projection.
- Không join cross-database; dùng application-level aggregation.

## Social-specific Business Rules
- Post visibility: `PUBLIC` (ai cũng xem), `FOLLOWERS` (chỉ follower với status `ACCEPTED`).
- Không hiển thị post có `status = DRAFT` hoặc `status = DELETED`.
- User `SUSPENDED/DELETED` không được tạo social action mới.
- Follow relation: unique `(follower_id, followee_id)`, không được tự follow.
- Like/Save: idempotent, unique `(post_id, user_id)`.
- Comment reaction: unique `(comment_id, user_id)`.

## Outbox Events MVP
- Publish: `POST_LIKED`, `COMMENT_CREATED`, `USER_FOLLOWED`.
- Consume from Auth: `USER_CREATED`, `USER_UPDATED`, `USER_DELETED`.
- Mọi event publish ra broker phải đi qua `OUTBOX_EVENTS`.

## Key MongoDB Indexes (MVP)
- `POSTS(status, visibility, created_at desc)`
- `POSTS(author_id, status, created_at desc)`
- `POSTS(hashtags)`
- `COMMENTS(post_id, status, created_at)`

## Key PostgreSQL Indexes (MVP)
- `FOLLOWS(follower_id, created_at desc)`
- `FOLLOWS(followee_id)`
- `SEARCH_HISTORY(user_id, created_at desc)`
